Goal Representation:
Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['1. Put dish soap in the dishwasher.', '2. Wash the bowls and plates using the dishwasher.']

behavior load_dishwasher_with_soap(dishwasher: item, soap: item):
    body:
        achieve open(dishwasher) # Ensure the dishwasher is open before loading soap
        achieve inside(soap, dishwasher) # Place the soap inside the dishwasher

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        
        bind soap: item where:
            is_detergent(soap)
        # Select dish soap
        
        load_dishwasher_with_soap(dishwasher, soap) # Load the dishwasher with soap

behavior put_dish_soap_in_dishwasher(dish_soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(dish_soap, dishwasher)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
        # Select dish soap

        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select the dishwasher

        put_dish_soap_in_dishwasher(dish_soap, dishwasher)

Reset goals: The sub-goals are:

behavior add_dish_soap(dish_soap:item, dishwasher:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(dish_soap, dishwasher)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
        # Select a dish soap
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        add_dish_soap(dish_soap, dishwasher)
        # Add the dish soap to the dishwasher

Reset goals: The sub-goals are:

behavior __goal__():

        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select the dishwasher

        bind dish_soap: item where:
            is_soap(dish_soap)
